reviewText: I received the wrong one not level 3..very disappointed
We have several exercise tapes but the class really loves this tape.  If they had their way we would use it everyday at our class.

Package arrived quickly and in good shape, however the video itself is unwatchable. I played the entire tape and constantly adjusting tracking to no avail. Picture rolled the entire time and was unwatchable. Disappointed.

I ordered 2 Nutri System Body Breakthrough: Activity Plan video tapes: Level 1 & 2 (together on a single tape) and Level 3.  I neglected to carefully examine my shipment before I destroyed the accompanying receipt.  I received 2 of the Level 1&2 tapes instead of one of each.  If you ever order from this merchant double check your order upon receipt!!
